{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-jsx","path":"/post/anime/ore-no-kanojo-to-osananajimi-ga-shuraba-sugiru-anime-one","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/84cc5/cover.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 106.74846625766872%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Cover\"\n        title=\"Cover\"\n        src=\"/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/a6d36/cover.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/222b7/cover.png 163w,\n/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/ff46a/cover.png 325w,\n/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/a6d36/cover.png 650w,\n/static/92c1219a38a14758eef062a561fff760/84cc5/cover.png 898w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>輕小說版的「我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場」(俺の彼女と幼なじみが修羅場すぎる)是還沒有看過啦，其實還沒看過的輕小說多著呢。而在這個時間裡，一部一部輕小說改編的動畫正一集一集的上演。</p>\n<p>「我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場」最吸引我去看的原因是舒服又偏淡的畫風，應該說，畫面彷彿籠罩在一股薄薄的白霧之中。這使得「夏川真涼」這為角色(上圖右上方)在畫面裡更加搶眼。頭髮好白呀！快要被閃瞎了。</p>\n<h3>以下是劇情簡介：</h3>\n<span style=\"color: #693\">\n<blockquote>\n<p> 主人公季堂鋭太是個成績優秀的高中生，理想是考入醫學院。一天同班同學夏川真涼向他告白，雖然他一開始拒絕了真涼，可是後來真涼用公開他初中時的日記本相脅迫，銳太只好答應和真涼交往。</p>\n<p> 而他的青梅竹馬春咲千和卻不認可真涼，導致夾在兩人之間的銳太十分困擾。兩位女主角性格都非常鮮明，一位是略有腹黑的頭腦派，一位則是豬突猛進的行動派，被這樣兩位玩弄在手的男主角，是幸運還是不幸呢，故事即將展開……</p>\n</blockquote>\n</span>\n \n<h3>第一集觀後心得<span style=\"color: red\">(注意有劇透)</span>：</h3>\n<p>輕小說版的「我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場」就已經透露出畫風乾淨潔白的感覺了，動畫部份整體而言有營造出輕小說封面上的感覺。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/770f765da68dbc14eb771bfd98a6d9f9/066f9/novel-cover.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Novel cover\"\n        title=\"Novel cover\"\n        src=\"/static/770f765da68dbc14eb771bfd98a6d9f9/066f9/novel-cover.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/770f765da68dbc14eb771bfd98a6d9f9/d2f63/novel-cover.jpg 163w,\n/static/770f765da68dbc14eb771bfd98a6d9f9/c989d/novel-cover.jpg 325w,\n/static/770f765da68dbc14eb771bfd98a6d9f9/066f9/novel-cover.jpg 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>當然，我沒拜讀過小說，所以對於動畫部分有沒有忠於原著，以及之後的劇情是否精彩？沒有辦法下定論。之後會不會把它看完，或者看到中途就不繼續追了？這也很難講。</p>\n<p>但對於第一集，我的印象還不錯。</p>\n<p>首當其衝的就是乾淨的畫面啦。劇情推移的速度也很快，沒有多餘的部分。</p>\n<p>劇情也很有趣，雖然目前出現了兩位女主角，之後似乎還兩位會出來。一心只想讀書考國立醫大的主角也真辛苦(笑)，如果這樣能譜出一段美麗的戀愛物語也不錯啦！花點分數去換我相信是值得的。</p>\n<p>劇情一開始，多多少少就注意到男主角有點「過去中二病」的感覺，會用過去來形容就是因為當下已經擺過過去中二的自己了。正因為如此，才會有許多有趣的事情。相信有看過「中二病也要談戀愛」的人會很快就適應的。</p>\n<p>這點果然很快就變成了把柄啊......</p>\n<p>首先是主角的青梅竹馬：「春咲千和」</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/2bef9/girl-one.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"春咲千和\"\n        title=\"春咲千和\"\n        src=\"/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/a6d36/girl-one.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/222b7/girl-one.png 163w,\n/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/ff46a/girl-one.png 325w,\n/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/a6d36/girl-one.png 650w,\n/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/e548f/girl-one.png 975w,\n/static/98d2977bea42031e8b8f518343e18a89/2bef9/girl-one.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>青梅竹馬外加鄰家女孩還真是王道的設定呀！但是感覺小小一隻的，果然聯想到青梅竹馬就會是蘿莉向嗎？</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/2bef9/girl-one-with-boy.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"春咲千和\"\n        title=\"春咲千和\"\n        src=\"/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/a6d36/girl-one-with-boy.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/222b7/girl-one-with-boy.png 163w,\n/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/ff46a/girl-one-with-boy.png 325w,\n/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/a6d36/girl-one-with-boy.png 650w,\n/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/e548f/girl-one-with-boy.png 975w,\n/static/e35dea266c0f7b32749f21934a678f7b/2bef9/girl-one-with-boy.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>「春咲千和」與男主角的互動從一剛開始就相當和平，配合優美的ＢＧＭ真的相當溫馨。</p>\n<p>只是「春咲千和」喜歡吃肉到瘋狂的境界，只要主角煮肉給她吃，就會相當高興...怎麼感覺好像在青梅竹馬與鄰家女孩之外又加上了寵物女孩的屬性啦？</p>\n<p>第一集出現的另一位主要女角色：「夏川真涼」</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/2bef9/girl-two.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"夏川真涼\"\n        title=\"夏川真涼\"\n        src=\"/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/a6d36/girl-two.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/222b7/girl-two.png 163w,\n/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/ff46a/girl-two.png 325w,\n/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/a6d36/girl-two.png 650w,\n/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/e548f/girl-two.png 975w,\n/static/5abcf5566a70f3e1ecb0ce459f43d793/2bef9/girl-two.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>乾淨又偏白的畫面跟這個角色有夠搭配的。白色的頭髮與白皮膚，加上學校白色制服與偏淡的白色畫風，彷彿看到的白色的天使一般，雖然之後發現的的個性並非如此就是了(笑)。</p>\n<p>才第一集沒多久，「夏川真涼」就對主角告白了。「夏川真涼」，歸國女子，受到男生追求，平均一天會被告白一次以上。被這樣的人告白，男主角之後的日子一定不好過吧。</p>\n<p>不過很諷刺的，正因為在校被熱烈的追求，「夏川真涼」才會向「對戀愛沒興趣」的男主角告白呀。</p>\n<p>事實證明，「粉紅的切開都是黑的」似乎也可以套用在白頭髮上面。</p>\n<p>看來白色切開也不會乾淨到哪裡去......</p>\n<p>後面就看「夏川真涼」展現可愛卻銳利的真性情。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/2bef9/girl-two-with-boy.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"夏川真涼\"\n        title=\"夏川真涼\"\n        src=\"/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/a6d36/girl-two-with-boy.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/222b7/girl-two-with-boy.png 163w,\n/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/ff46a/girl-two-with-boy.png 325w,\n/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/a6d36/girl-two-with-boy.png 650w,\n/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/e548f/girl-two-with-boy.png 975w,\n/static/e9fa91dc7f0469cda85546e5712555a0/2bef9/girl-two-with-boy.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>堅持不談戀愛的男主角就被這位「天使外表，惡魔內在」女孩攻略了。</p>\n<p>所以說，中二時期的筆記什麼的，果然是危險的東西呀！</p>\n<p>我連挖出以前寫在筆記本上的小說來看，都會羞愧的想鑽到地上的洞裡去了>///&#x3C;</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/2bef9/boy-scream.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Boy Scream\"\n        title=\"Boy Scream\"\n        src=\"/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/a6d36/boy-scream.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/222b7/boy-scream.png 163w,\n/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/ff46a/boy-scream.png 325w,\n/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/a6d36/boy-scream.png 650w,\n/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/e548f/boy-scream.png 975w,\n/static/0feb650b5790a21962ddaafa23275fd0/2bef9/boy-scream.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>果然，自己造的孽，要自己扛下來呀。</p>\n<p>加油吧！「季堂鋭太」。</p>\n<p>正因為過去中二，才顯得現在的自己成熟。</p>\n<p>正因為踏錯那一步，未來才多了無限的無法預知的可能。</p>\n<p>目前興致高昂，期待下一集。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 05, 2013","slug":"/anime/ore-no-kanojo-to-osananajimi-ga-shuraba-sugiru-anime-one","title":"動畫 - 我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場 - 動畫版＆第一集","tags":"動畫, 心得, 我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場","hot":true}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/anime/ore-no-kanojo-to-osananajimi-ga-shuraba-sugiru-anime-one"}}}